text: San Miguel Partido is a partido in the Greater Buenos Aires urban area of Buenos Aires Province in Argentina. Provisional results of the 2010 census report that the provincial subdivision has a population of about 281,120 inhabitants in an area of . Its capital city is San Miguel, which is around from Buenos Aires. ==Districts== * Bella Vista * Campo de Mayo * Muñiz * San Miguel ==References== ==External links== *San Miguel (Spanish) Category:1994 establishments in Argentina Category:Partidos of Buenos Aires Province
